*   备注
    
    yum install -y gol运行有问题，
    
    Dockerfile修改如下
    
    \# install golang
    
    RUN rpm -ivh https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
    
    RUN yum install -y golang
    
    参考:
    
    https://studygolang.com/articles/17027
    
    https://www.sudops.com/cengos-install-golang-env-in-three-ways.html
    

